query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(q1 s t1 tq1 u1 a1) */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 0 AND q1.favorite_count <= 1
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('gis',
'mathoverflow',
'pt')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.upvotes >= 10 AND u1.upvotes <= 1000000
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('android',
'arcgis-10.0',
'arcmap',
'at.algebraic-topology',
'coordinate-system',
'css',
'dg.differential-geometry',
'gdal',
'gr.group-theory',
'jquery',
'linear-algebra',
'mysql',
'pr.probability',
'rt.representation-theory',
'sql')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND a1.question_id = q1.id group by t1.name;
